This music video is a reflection of who we are — not just as a band, but as people who’ve been through so much together. No characters, no complex narratives — just us. 

For the first time, Gab, CJ, and Xen share their voices, Gian steps into his directorial debut, and Rapha helped shape the concept from the very beginning.
